Description: Update DAEMON Tools Pro Advanced Edition - software for emulating virtual drive on operating systems Windows 2000/XP/Vista (supports both 32 - and 64-bit system). The program installs a special driver in the system by which Windows detects a virtual drive and can work with him as with the ordinary. The only difference is that instead of these laser discs using a CD image file and DVD-media. DAEMON Tools works through a system tray menu with which you get access to all its commands.
